      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 122,
      "message": "You are scanning the end of the string twice (contains() and lastIndexOf(), This can be changed to:\n\nint dotLocation = anyString.lastIndexOf(\".\");\nif (dotLocation != -1) {\n  value = anyString.substring(dotLocation + 1);",
